bignum = require("browserify-bignum");
uuid = require("node-uuid");
_ = require("underscore");
_s = require("underscore.string");

//---------------------------------------------------------------------------


_dicomDictionaryString = ""

/**
 * Creates a '2.25' style dicom UID
 * Returns a string.
 */
exports.uid = function() {
  var bytes = uuid.parse(uuid.v4());
  var idNumber = new bignum(0);
  var two = new bignum(2);

  for (var i = 0; i < bytes.length; i++) {
    var contribution = new bignum(bytes[i]);
    var shifted = contribution.times(two.toPower(8*i));
    idNumber = idNumber.plus(shifted);
  }
  return "2.25." + idNumber.toString(10);
}

/**
 * make an easy-to-access dictionary
 */
exports._parseDictionary = function(dictionaryString) {
  // TODO: if this proves too time consuming, save out the
  // pre-filled index arrays.
  exports.dictionary = {};
  exports.dictionary.keywordByTag = {};
  exports.dictionary.vrByTag = {};
  exports.dictionary.vmByTag = {};
  exports.dictionary.versionByTag = {};
  exports.dictionary.tagByKeyword = {};
  _.each(_s.lines(dictionaryString), function(line, index, list) {
    if (!_s.startsWith(line, '#')) {
      words = _s.words(line);
      tag = words[0].replace('(','').replace(')','').replace(',','');
      keyword = words[2]
      exports.dictionary.tagByKeyword[keyword] = tag;
      exports.dictionary.vrByTag[tag] = words[1];
      exports.dictionary.vmByTag[tag] = words[3];
      exports.dictionary.versionByTag[tag] = words[4];
    }
  });
}


var testing = false; // TODO: use a testing package like mocha

if (testing) {
  console.log(exports.uid());
